or external WebDAV server is required; focus on in-process coverage of XML/DAV method construction, headers, reports, properties, and servlet-facing adapters using lightweight mocks or stubs. Use javax.servlet-era APIs, not jakarta.servlet.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The library is old and uses pre-Jakarta javax.servlet APIs; using jakarta.servlet would not compile.\",\n    \"A missing SLF4J binding may produce warnings but is not required for meaningful coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00855e3aa7250c2e016a41f6d13c8c819394c9e6d5f230bd51\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 806, "output": 1322, "cacheRead": 35840, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 37968, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782707906838, "responseId": "resp_00855e3aa7250c2e016a41f6c375148193a6b3c4d043e4d788"}, "toolResults": []}
